{"tid":2504014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基叫林家謙千祈唔好縮 取笑不善辭令答乜都死","createTime":"2021-04-25T13:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:36:10.000Z","uid":58335,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9449da44bb41169f102e80a6ffc4aaefa2db712c","tid":2504014,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"連登仔又要反埋鄭中基<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢老盲撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林家謙獨唱《一人之境》，兩人合唱《我代你哭》，鄭中基將林家謙攞獎被指黑面一事開玩笑，玩嘢問：「聽講問你嘢，答時會講錯嘢？咁多人支持你開唔開心？」林家謙答：「開心，真㗎。」鄭中基再問林家謙未來計劃，卻又自說自話：「你都係唔好答，答有，就話你有機心，答冇，就話你冷（Cool）。不如問你有冇拍拖？都係唔好答，有就話你掛住拍拖，冇就話你講大話。」<br />\n<br />\n接住才入正題，鄭中基問到好想知《一人之境》是誰創作？觀眾帶出作曲、填詞、編曲、監製均是林家謙，鄭中基叫林家謙要多謝自己4次，林家謙即謙虛講四次多謝，然後怕醜地退後，鄭中基見狀笑說：「你千祈唔好縮，等我呢個老嘢縮，你好好哋做好音樂就得喇。」林家謙很開心成為演唱會嘉賓，並說：「第一次喺咁空曠，有浮雲、街。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210425/EQR5OD5GOBD6RKTD7AYV32L2W4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210425%2FEQR5OD5GOBD6RKTD7AYV32L2W4%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=367843c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210425%2FEQR5OD5GOBD6RKTD7AYV32L2W4%2F&h=35cfbd58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210425/EQR5OD5GOBD6RKTD7AYV32L2W4/</a>"},{"pid":"b0021f2eab7aceb6efe8eb2a0cbfc1d68f484493","tid":2504014,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aece074bcf7addd490e6206acdd09fca39d0650a","tid":2504014,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:01:38.000Z","ms